	,"x4freetext":[" Measurements between 15 and 165 deg. were"
		,"taken with an array of four surface-barrier detectors"
		,"mounted on the cart assembly with separations of 5"
		,"deg.. Measurements at angles beyond 165 deg. were"
		,"made using two surface-barrier, position-sensitive"
		,"detectors (1x3 cm, 600-mu-m thick) ."]
	}
